 sud de l'Italie. Un certain nombre de ses photographies ont été publiées dans le numéro de mars 1952 du Courrier de l'UNESCO avec un article de Carlo Levi, dont le roman Le Christ s'est arrêté à Eboli (1945) lui avait valu une renommée internationale  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aModern history, 1453-. 7aHISTORY / Study & Teaching.2bisacsh1 aAzoulay, Audrey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHendel, Giovanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHendel, Giovanna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLengrand, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeda, Juri, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNaggar, Carole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNaggar, Carole, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPriem, Karin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPriem, Karin, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2020z978311069628808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCz978311065906108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTi